# MSW DataSet CSVs: the MSW Maker re-saves them with a UTF-8 BOM while agent
# scripts write them without one. Strip the BOM on the way into the repo so the
# stored blob is always identical regardless of which tool last wrote the file.
# Requires a one-time local config on each machine:
#   git config filter.msw-stripbom.clean "node scripts/git-stripbom.cjs"
*.csv filter=msw-stripbom
